targets.query: SELECT sum("clients.total") *$time_save/$time_group AS "Clients", count("load") *$time_save/$time_group AS "Node" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[time_group]]s) fill(null)

SELECT non_negative_derivative(sum("traffic.rx.bytes"), 1s) AS "down", non_negative_derivative(sum("traffic.tx.bytes"), 1s) *-1 AS "up" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /^$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(none)

SELECT mean("load") AS "Load",  ((mean("memory.total")-mean("memory.free"))/mean("memory.total")) AS "Memory Usage" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("airtime11g.chan_util") *$time_save/$time_group AS "2.4 Ghz", mean("airtime11a.chan_util") *$time_save/$time_group AS "5 Ghz" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time([[time_group]]s) fill(null)

SELECT sum("clients.total") AS "Clients", sum("clients.wifi") AS "Wifi", sum("clients.wifi5") AS "5Ghz", count("load") AS "Node" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
SELECT sum("neighbours.total") AS "Total", sum("neighbours.vpn") AS "VPN" FROM "node" WHERE "nodeid" =~ /$node$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
